There are 3 different nationalities: egyptian, indian, russian
The people's birthday is in 3 different months: december, july, august
The people prefer 3 different types of sport: climbing, sailing, swimming
 1. the person eating kale is the person who's birthday is in july##1
 2. the russian is the person who's hobby is magic-tricks##1
 3. the person watching adventure movies is the person eating peas##1
 4. the person watching satire movies is the person who's birthday is in july##1
 5. the person who's sport is sailing is on the left of the person who's sport is swimming##1
 6. the person watching satire movies is on the left of the person who's sport is swimming##1
 7. the person who's hobby is skydiving is between the indian and the fan of r&b##2
 8. the indian is on the left of the fan of folk##1
 9. the person who's birthday is in july is on the right of the person who's sport is climbing##1
10. the person who's birthday is in august is on the right of the person eating kale##1
11. the indian is the person eating peas##1

