 1. the person who's sport is water-polo is in the middle##1
 2. the person drinking fanta is in the middle##1
 3. the fan of country is on the right of the person who's hobby is drawing##1
 4. the person who's hobby is singing is the person watching disaster movies##1
 5. the person driving the subway is on the right of the fan of country##1
 6. the owner of the guinea-pig is on the left of the person watching disaster movies##1
 7. the person driving the van is between the person drinking almond-milk and the fan of classical##2
 8. the person watching adventure movies is on the right of the person who's sport is handball##1
 9. the person watching disaster movies is the person driving the subway##1
10. the owner of the guinea-pig is on the left of the owner of the fish##1
11. the person driving the subway is the fan of classical##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |     2      |    3     |
| Beverage      | almond-milk | fanta      | tea      |
| Hobby         | drawing     | hiking     | singing  |
| Movie-Genre   | documentary | adventure  | disaster |
| Music-Genre   | d&b  | country     | classical |
| Pet           | bird        | guinea-pig | fish     |
| Sport         | handball    | water-polo | soccer   |
| Transport     | taxi        | van        | subway   |

