.:: Puzzle 7x3-Level-2-18::.
There are 3 different favourite beverages: fanta, juice, milk
There 3 different types of food: broccoli, mango, pumpkin
The people grow 3 different varities of flowers: daisy, iris, poppy
The people have 3 different jobs:  dressmaker, manager, musician
The people perfer 3 different movie-genres: epic, fantasy, mystery
The people prefer 3 different types of sport: rugby, surfing, water-polo
The people use 3 different means of transport: helicopter, ship, skateboard
1. the person drinking juice is on the left of the musician##1
2. the person driving the skateboard is on the right of the person eating pumpkin##1
3. the person eating mango is on the left of the dressmaker##1
4. the person who's sport is rugby is between the person watching epic movies and the manager##2
5. the person eating pumpkin is between the musician and the person who growspoppy##2
6. the person who growsiris is on the right of the person eating pumpkin##1
7. the person who's sport is surfing is on the right of the person drinking juice##1
8. the person driving the helicopter is on the left of the person drinking milk##1
9. the person watching fantasy movies is on the left of the dressmaker##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |     2      |     3      |
| Beverage      | fanta      | juice      | milk       |
| Food          | mango      | pumpkin    | broccoli   |
| Flower         | poppy    | daisy     | iris     |
| Job           | manager    | dressmaker | musician   |
| Movie-Genre   | fantasy    | mystery    | epic       |
| Sport         | water-polo | rugby      | surfing    |
| Transport     | ship       | helicopter | skateboard |

